
Task
Is the function argument an array?
Write a function isArgArray that takes value as an argument and returns true if value is an array and false otherwise. Use the Array.isArray () method when solving.
Example:
• the isArgArray (123) function must return false;
• the isArgArray ("Welcome") function must return false;
• the isArgArray (true) function must return false;
• the isArgArray ([]) function must return true;
• the isArgArray ({name: 'Alice'}) function must return false;
• the isArgArray (null) function must return false;
• the isArgArray (undefined) function must return false;
• the isArgArray ([1,2,3,4]) function must return true.

Solution
function isArgArray (value) {
 if (Array.isArray (value)) return true;
  return false;
}
